@ExpenseTracker_HostAddress = http://localhost:5037
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ?? Auth ??

### Google Login (paste a Google ID token)
POST {{ExpenseTracker_HostAddress}}/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "PASTE_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_HERE"
}

###

### ?? Categories ??

### Get all categories
GET {{ExpenseTracker_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a category
POST {{ExpenseTracker_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Food",
  "icon": "??",
  "color": "#ef4444"
}

###

### ?? Expenses ??

### Get all expenses (paginated)
GET {{ExpenseTracker_HostAddress}}/api/expenses?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create an expense
POST {{ExpenseTracker_HostAddress}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Lunch",
  "amount": 15.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "category": "Food",
  "note": "Office lunch"
}

###

### Get expense summary (current month)
GET {{ExpenseTracker_HostAddress}}/api/expenses/summary
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
